<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Intelligence Challenge — Technical Track</title>
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --ink: #0A0F1E;
  --ink-mid: #2E3650;
  --ink-light: #6B7494;
  --rule: #D0D4E4;
  --bg: #F4F5F9;
  --surface: #FFFFFF;
  --signal: #0E2D6B;
  --signal-mid: #1A4DA8;
  --signal-lt: #E8EDF8;
  --signal-rule: #B5C8F4;
  --warn: #7A4500;
  --warn-lt: #FDF5E6;
  --gold: #7A5200;
  --gold-lt: #FDF6E3;
  --green: #1A5C38;
  --green-lt: #E6EFE9;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  min-height: 100vh;
}

.page {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: var(--surface);
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding: 52px 48px 72px;
}

.masthead {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: start;
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  border-bottom: 3px solid var(--signal);
}

.eyebrow {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--signal-mid);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 38px;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1.05;
  color: var(--ink);
}

h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--signal-mid); }

.tagline {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  margin-top: 8px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.contact {
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.8;
  padding-top: 4px;
}

.contact strong { display: block; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); font-size: 13px; }
.contact a { color: var(--signal-mid); text-decoration: none; }

.honest-bar {
  background: var(--warn-lt);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--warn);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.honest-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--warn);
  white-space: nowrap;
  padding-top: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.honest-text {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.opening-box {
  background: var(--signal-lt);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--signal-mid);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.opening-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--signal-mid);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.opening-text {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-style: italic;
}

.signal-bar {
  background: var(--signal);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.signal-bar-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  white-space: nowrap;
  padding-top: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.signal-bar-text {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.65;
}

.sh {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding-bottom: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.weeks {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr);
  gap: 0;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.week {
  padding: 14px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.week:last-child { border-right: none; }

.week.hl {
  background: var(--signal-lt);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--signal-mid);
}

.wnum {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--signal-mid);
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.wtitle {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.wdesc {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.wtag {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  background: var(--signal);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 2px 6px;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.col {
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 16px;
}

.col.dark { background: var(--signal); border-color: var(--signal); }

.col-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.col.dark .col-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

.col-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.5;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.col-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.col-item-m {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  background: var(--signal-mid);
  margin-top: 1px;
}

.col.dark .col-item { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

.pricing {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.price-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 16px;
}

.price-card.pilot {
  border: 2px solid var(--signal-mid);
  background: var(--signal-lt);
}

.price-tier {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.price-card.pilot .price-tier { color: var(--signal-mid); }

.price-title {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.price-amount {
  font-size: 26px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--signal);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1;
}

.price-note {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.price-item {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  padding: 4px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.price-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.price-item::before { content: '→'; color: var(--signal-mid); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }

.diagnostic {
  background: var(--green-lt);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--green);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: center;
}

.diag-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--green);
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.diag-title {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.diag-text {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.55;
}

.diag-cta {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  background: var(--green);
  padding: 10px 18px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.brief-footer {
  border-top: 3px solid var(--signal);
  padding-top: 18px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-end;
  gap: 20px;
}

.footer-quote {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--ink);
  max-width: 380px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.footer-contact {
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.8;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.footer-contact a { color: var(--signal-mid); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }

@media(max-width:640px){
  .page { padding: 32px 20px 48px; }
  .masthead { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .weeks { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .pricing { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .diagnostic { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .brief-footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

<div class="masthead">
  <div>
    <div class="eyebrow">Intelligence Challenge · Technical Track · Pilot Programme · ADAS · SDV</div>
    <h1>The <em>Intelligence</em> Sprint</h1>
    <div class="tagline">A 4-week pilot that surfaces technical insights with commercial value from ADAS and SDV engineering teams — and creates a structured pathway to product management.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="contact">
    <strong>Keithan Cokbilir</strong>
    LXD Advisory<br>
    hello@keithan.eu<br>
    <a href="https://keithan-c.github.io/Keithan-s_lxd_portfolio">Portfolio</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="honest-bar">
  <div class="honest-label">A word first</div>
  <div class="honest-text">This is a pilot programme. The design, the scoreboard, the insight brief template, and the measurement framework are all built and ready. What it hasn't done yet is run inside a real engineering organisation. That's what this pilot is for. You get a full facilitated programme at a significant discount. I get a real case study with your team's data. That's the deal, stated plainly.</div>
</div>

<div class="opening-box">
  <div class="opening-label">Why I'm reaching out to your team specifically</div>
  <div class="opening-text">"Your engineers understand technical feasibility, platform limitations, and supplier capability in granular detail that product management and business development rarely see. That intelligence gap has a cost — in missed decisions, in slow cycles, in ideas that surface too late. This programme closes it."</div>
</div>

<div class="signal-bar">
  <div class="signal-bar-label">The gap</div>
  <div class="signal-bar-text">ADAS and SDV engineering teams sit on technically and commercially valuable intelligence about sensor performance, platform architecture trade-offs, and supplier capability gaps. Right now that intelligence reaches product management through formal reviews that are too slow, too filtered, and too late to drive real decisions.</div>
</div>

<div class="sh">How the pilot works — 4 weeks</div>
<div class="weeks">
  <div class="week">
    <div class="wnum">Week 1</div>
    <div class="wtitle">Anchor to a live programme</div>
    <div class="wdesc">Each team identifies a current engineering programme, platform, or supplier their insight connects to. No data required yet.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="week">
    <div class="wnum">Week 2</div>
    <div class="wtitle">Insight brief submitted</div>
    <div class="wdesc">Teams submit a structured insight brief — context, technical observation, commercial or regulatory implication. Scoreboard goes live.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="week hl">
    <div class="wnum">Week 3</div>
    <div class="wtitle">Data strengthens the brief</div>
    <div class="wdesc">A one-page job aid releases — three data views that translate engineering metrics into a commercial argument. Released when teams have a real question.</div>
    <div class="wtag">Design decision</div>
  </div>
  <div class="week">
    <div class="wnum">Week 4</div>
    <div class="wtitle">Review day</div>
    <div class="wdesc">Top 3 insights presented to product management and leadership. Winner enters a 6-week development pathway with a named product manager as owner.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="two-col">
  <div class="col">
    <div class="col-label">What the pilot produces</div>
    <div class="col-item"><div class="col-item-m">1</div>3–5 structured insight briefs ready for product management review</div>
    <div class="col-item"><div class="col-item-m">2</div>One winning insight entering a 6-week development pathway with a named PM owner</div>
    <div class="col-item"><div class="col-item-m">3</div>A documented case study with your team's real outcome data — owned by you</div>
    <div class="col-item"><div class="col-item-m">4</div>Reduced cycle time from engineering observation to commercial brief</div>
  </div>
  <div class="col dark">
    <div class="col-label">What I need from you</div>
    <div class="col-item" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">An ADAS, SDV, or systems engineering team of 8–30 people</div>
    <div class="col-item" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">A product management contact willing to receive and act on the insight briefs</div>
    <div class="col-item" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">Access to one data tool the team already uses for technical reporting</div>
    <div class="col-item" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">Permission to document the outcome as a named case study</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sh">Investment — three options, one honest conversation</div>
<div class="pricing">
  <div class="price-card pilot">
    <div class="price-tier">Pilot — one slot open</div>
    <div class="price-title">Full facilitation</div>
    <div class="price-amount">€2,500</div>
    <div class="price-note">Pilot price. Full programme. One organisation per track. In exchange for a documented case study with real outcome data.</div>
    <div class="price-item">Design tailored to your engineering context</div>
    <div class="price-item">Live insight scoreboard built and managed</div>
    <div class="price-item">4-week facilitation by Keithan</div>
    <div class="price-item">Review day with product management panel</div>
    <div class="price-item">6-week development pathway for winning insight</div>
    <div class="price-item">Full case study documented</div>
  </div>
  <div class="price-card">
    <div class="price-tier">Standard — after pilot</div>
    <div class="price-title">Full facilitation</div>
    <div class="price-amount">€6,500</div>
    <div class="price-note">For subsequent organisations once one case study exists for the technical track.</div>
    <div class="price-item">Everything in pilot tier</div>
    <div class="price-item">Post-programme insight pipeline report</div>
    <div class="price-item">Full outcome data shared</div>
  </div>
  <div class="price-card">
    <div class="price-tier">Design only</div>
    <div class="price-title">Handover</div>
    <div class="price-amount">€3,500</div>
    <div class="price-note">You deliver internally. Available at any stage.</div>
    <div class="price-item">Full programme design</div>
    <div class="price-item">Insight scoreboard built</div>
    <div class="price-item">Facilitator guide</div>
    <div class="price-item">Data job aid — 3 views</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="diagnostic">
  <div>
    <div class="diag-label">Start here — free, no obligation</div>
    <div class="diag-title">60-minute diagnostic conversation</div>
    <div class="diag-text">Before anything else — a structured 60-minute conversation about your team's intelligence gap. I'll ask five questions about how technical insights currently reach product management. You'll leave with three specific design recommendations, regardless of whether we work together.</div>
  </div>
  <a class="diag-cta" href="mailto:hello@keithan.eu?subject=60-minute diagnostic — Intelligence Sprint">Book the call →</a>
</div>

<div class="brief-footer">
  <div class="footer-quote">"The intelligence already exists inside your engineering teams. The Sprint builds the pathway to surface it."</div>
  <div class="footer-contact">
    Keithan Cokbilir · LXD Advisory<br>
    <a href="mailto:hello@keithan.eu">hello@keithan.eu</a><br>
    Ingolstadt, Germany<br>
    <a href="https://keithan-c.github.io/Keithan-s_lxd_portfolio">Portfolio</a>
  </div>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
